    "en": {
      "title": "IMF Chief pleased by IMF staff level agreement",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); IMF Chief Kristalina Georgieva has stated that she is pleased that IMF staff and Sri Lankan government officials have reached a staff-level agreement to support the country\u2019s economic policies.",
        "The Sri Lankan Government and the IMF reached an agreement for a 48-month Extended Fund Facility of \u00a0US$ 2.9 billion recently.",
        "\"This is an important step forward for Sri Lanka,\" she stated."
      ],
